your recovery down significantly. We've put together everything you need to feel like yourself again.</p>\n<a href=\"https://bargainchemist.co.nz/collections/cold-flu\" style=\"background:#FF0031;color:#ffffff;font-size:15px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 36px;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;\">Shop Recovery Essentials</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<!-- \u2500\u2500 INTRO BODY \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 -->\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:36px 40px;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:16px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.7;\">Hi {{ first_name|default('there') }},</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#444444;font-size:15px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.7;\">Feeling rough? You're not alone \u2014 flu season is in full swing across New Zealand. The good news: with the right support your body can recover faster. Below are our pharmacist-backed tips and the products most people reach for when they're fighting off a cold or flu.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<!-- \u2500\u2500 DIVIDER \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 -->\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\"><hr style=\"border:0;border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;margin:0;\"/></td></tr>\n<!-- \u2500\u2500 RECOVERY TIPS \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 -->\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:32px 40px;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin:0 0 24px;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:20px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;text-align:center;\">3 Ways to Recover Faster</h2>\n<!-- Tip 1 -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"48\">\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"background:#FF0031;color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:bold;width:36px;height:36px;text-align:center;border-radius:50%;line-height:36px;\">1</td></tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:12px;\" valign=\"top\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:15px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:bold;\">Load up on Zinc &amp; Vitamin C early</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#555555;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;\">Both nutrients support your immune response and are most effective in the first 24\u201348 hours. Don't wait \u2014 start as soon as symptoms appear.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<!-- Tip 2 -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:20px;\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"48\">\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"background:#FF0031;color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:bold;width:36px;height:36px;text-align:center;border-radius:50%;line-height:36px;\">2</td></tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:12px;\" valign=\"top\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:15px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:bold;\">Manage symptoms so you can actually rest</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#555555;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;\">Sleep is when your immune system does its best work. A quality cold &amp; flu day/night formula helps you stay comfortable and get the rest you need.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<!-- Tip 3 -->\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\" width=\"48\">\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr><td style=\"background:#FF0031;color:#ffffff;font-size:18px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:bold;width:36px;height:36px;text-align:center;border-radius:50%;line-height:36px;\">3</td></tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-left:12px;\" valign=\"top\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:15px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-weight:bold;\">Rebuild after recovery with probiotics</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#555555;font-size:14px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;\">Illness (and antibiotics if prescribed) depletes good gut bacteria. A probiotic supports your gut health and helps rebuild your immune defences for next time.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<!-- \u2500\u2500 DIVIDER \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 -->\n<tr><td style=\"padding:0 40px;\"><hr style=\"border:0;border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;margin:0;\"/></td></tr>\n<!-- \u2500\u2500 SECTION HEADING \u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500 -->\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:32px 40px 16px;text-align:center;\">\n<h2 style=\"margin:0;color:#1a1a1a;font-size:20px;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">Recovery Essentials</h2>\n<p style=\"margin:8px 0 0;color:#666666;font-size:14px;font-family:Ari